# CAMERA_SOURCE Options:
# - "0" = Default/Built-in Webcam
# - "1" = External USB Camera (if connected)
# - "http://PHONE_IP:8080/video" = Android IP Webcam (Google Play)
# - "rtsp://PHONE_IP:PORT/stream" = iOS Reachability Camera or other RTSP streams
# 
# For Android Phone Camera via IP Webcam:
# 1. Install "IP Webcam" app from Google Play
# 2. Start the server in app (default port 8080)
# 3. Find your phone IP: Settings > About > IP Address
# 4. Use: CAMERA_SOURCE=http://192.168.x.x:8080/video
#
# For iPhone via RTSP:
# 1. Use apps like "Reachability Camera" or "FileMic"
# 2. Get RTSP stream URL from app settings
# 3. Use: CAMERA_SOURCE=rtsp://192.168.x.x:PORT/stream